## params to allow smtp alerts over gmail (using 2025 gmail security policy)

Linux:
  APT deps:
    msmtp (apparmor is ok)
    mailutils
    
  Define  ~/.msmtprc (and chmod 600):
    account gmail
    auth on
    host smtp.gmail.com
    port 587
    protocol smtp
    tls on
    tls_starttls on
    tls_trust_file /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
    from example@gmail.com
    user example@gmail.com
    passwordeval "cat ~/.oauth_token"
    logfile ~/.msmtp.log

  At console.cloud.google.com, configure a OAuth2.0 client and export credentials.json
  
